```diff
+ export function isOAuthEnabled(): boolean {
+   return FEATURE_FLAGS.OAUTH_GOOGLE_ENABLED || FEATURE_FLAGS.OAUTH_FACEBOOK_ENABLED;
+ }
+ 
+ /**
+  * Get list of enabled OAuth providers
+  */
+ export function getEnabledOAuthProviders(): string[] {
+   const providers: string[] = [];
+   if (FEATURE_FLAGS.OAUTH_GOOGLE_ENABLED) providers.push("google");
+   if (FEATURE_FLAGS.OAUTH_FACEBOOK_ENABLED) providers.push("facebook");
+   return providers;
+ }
+ 
```

```diff
+   try {
+     const supabase = await createClient();
+ 
+     const { data, error } = await supabase.auth.signInWithOAuth({
+       provider,

+         redirectTo: &#96;${process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL || "http://localhost:3000"}/auth/callback&#96;,
+       },
+     });
+ 
+     if (error) {
+       console.error(&#96;[Auth] OAuth ${provider} sign in error:&#96;, error);
+       return {
+         success: false,
+         error: &#96;Failed to sign in with ${provider}. Please try again.&#96;,
+       };
+     }
+ 
+     if (data.url) {
+       redirect(data.url);
+     }
+ 
+     return {
+       success: false,
+       error: "OAuth flow did not return a redirect URL",
+     };
+   } catch (error) {
+     console.error(&#96;[Auth] OAuth ${provider} error:&#96;, error);
+     return {
+       success: false,
+       error: "An unexpected error occurred. Please try again.",
+     };
+   }
+ }
```

Lines added: 64, lines removed: 1

```diff
@@ -1,1 +1,64 @@
- 
+ import { NextRequest, NextResponse } from "next/server";
+ import { createClient } from "@/lib/supabase/server";
+ import { db } from "@/db";
+ import { profiles } from "@/db/schema";
+ import { eq } from "drizzle-orm";
+ 
+ /**
+  * OAuth Callback Handler
+  * 
+  * Handles the OAuth callback from Supabase after successful authentication.
+  * Creates a profile record if it doesn't exist and redirects to dashboard.
+  */
+ export async function GET(request: NextRequest): Promise&lt;NextResponse&gt; {
+   const requestUrl = new URL(request.url);
+   const code = requestUrl.searchParams.get("code");
+ 
+   if (code) {
+     const supabase = await createClient();
+ 
+     // Exchange code for session
+     const { data, error } = await supabase.auth.exchangeCodeForSession(code);
+ 
+     if (error) {
+       console.error("[Auth] OAuth callback error:", error);
+       return NextResponse.redirect(
+         new URL("/auth/login?error=oauth_failed", requestUrl.origin)
+       );
+     }
+ 
+     if (data.user) {
+       try {
+         // Check if profile exists
+         const existingProfile = await db
+           .select()
+           .from(profiles)
+           .where(eq(profiles.id, data.user.id))
+           .limit(1);
+ 
+         // Create profile if it doesn't exist
+         if (existingProfile.length === 0) {
+           await db.insert(profiles).values({
+             id: data.user.id,
+             email: data.user.email!,
+             subscriptionTier: "FREE",
+             createdAt: new Date(),
+           });
+         }
+ 
+         // Redirect to dashboard
+         return NextResponse.redirect(new URL("/dashboard", requestUrl.origin));
+       } catch (dbError) {
+         console.error("[Auth] Profile creation error:", dbError);
+         // Still redirect to dashboard - profile creation can be retried
+         return NextResponse.redirect(new URL("/dashboard", requestUrl.origin));
+       }
+     }
+   }
+ 
+   // No code or user - redirect to login with error
+   return NextResponse.redirect(
+     new URL("/auth/login?error=oauth_failed", requestUrl.origin)
+   );
+ }
+ 
```
